Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.47,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,.أكيد
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.03,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,.ها أنا قادم
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.05,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,لن ألتحق
